Popular Movies App Part 1
Popular Movies App Part 1
Added network exception TextView
Added network exception TextView
Added network exception TextView
First commit
Test commit and push
Test commit and push
Implemented suggestions from Part 1 project review
Added calls for getVideos and getReviews to MovieApiInterface
Detail activity layout changes to include views for trailer and reviews
Add Review, ReviewResults, Trailer, and TrailerResults classes
Make API calls to get list of trailers and reviews in DetailActivity
Created TextViews and onClickListeners for trailers and reviews in the Detail activity
Populated TextViews for trailers and reviews if data is available in the Detail activity
Fixed NullPointerException in onResponse() methods in DetailActivity
Created ReviewActivity and TrailerActivity
Display movie reviews in ReviewActivity
Display trailer items in TrailerActivity
Added intent to play trailers on YouTube
Started using Room library to store favorite movies (created entity, Dao, database, and repository, and added onClickListener to insert/delete movies and update star icon color in DetailActivity)
Started using LiveData, added Favorites menu option and populated MainActivity with favorites when selected, used intent extra to pass data for favorite movies to FavoritesActivity

Added getMovieDetails query to Dao, passed movie id in intent to FavoritesActivity to use getMovieDetails to retrieve the movie rather than passing movie as parcelable, and generated favoritesPicturePathList in populateGridWithFavorites in MainActivity after onChanged so that the UI updates when a favorite is added or removed

Replaced getMovieDetails(int id) which returned LiveData<Movie> with getMovie(int id) which returns Movie to get movie to populate FavoritesActivity and used LiveData and diskIO executor to query database on background thread.
Used getPosterPath() from Movie class rather than getPosterPath() from Dao and removed unused queries from Dao
Previous code restored - incorrect movies were being displayed in FavoritesActivity
Added LiveData<Movie> to Dao and FavoritesActivity

Added LiveData<int[]> to Dao, FavoritesActivity, and DetailActivity. When viewing a movie in FavoritesActivity, app crashes after the movie has been removed from favorites and added back to favorites (movie returned is null).
Updated updateFavorites to fix thread-pool/NullPointer exception
Fixed errors in FavoritesActivity
Removed allowMainThreadQueries() from MovieRoomDatabase
Added ViewModel so that database is not queried again on rotation
Cleaned project
Removed API key and cleaned project
Restored onSavedInstanceState in onCreate method in DetailActivity and TrailerActivity so that movie posters and trailer are displayed after rotation when internet connection is lost

Added an if statement to check that there is an app (web browser) to handle request (launch YouTube trailer) in TrailerAdapter and added android:launchMode = "singleTop" to manifest to save state when pressing up button.
